::DarkMouse::

She stood next to Quickstrike in mouse mode.  She looked a the sphere 
wondering what was going on.  She saw the bot, who looked like 
HellBeast step out of the ship.  She felt a twinge of fear and anger 
flow through her.  Why was this bot the one to decide who lived and 
died?  Why was he the one playing the Matrix?   She wanted to turn 
him into scrap.  But she knew she had better hold tight and wait to 
see what happened before jumping into something.   Megatron was one 
thing, but this was something totally different.
She stayed in mouse mode and twitched her whiskers.  She didn't like 
this at all.
